hL._note: coefficients are in increasing order; input in K, output in J/mol; value is enthalpy minus hs_anchor enthalpy

hLV._note: coefficients are in increasing order; input in K, output in J/mol; value is enthalpy minus hs_anchor enthalpy

melting_line._note: Modified coefficients to make minimum state agree with triple point and increased Tmax to 230.3 K to allow pmax of EOS

sL._note: coefficients are in increasing order; input in K, output in J/mol/K; value is entropy minus hs_anchor entropy

sLV._note: coefficients are in increasing order; input in K, output in J/mol/K; value is entropy minus hs_anchor entropy

crit_anc._note: coefficients are for the function like ln(|rho^A-rhoc|) = sum_i c_i ln(Theta)^i with Theta=(Tc-T)/Tc

critical_region_splines._note: Coefficients for the critical cubic spline.  T = c[0]*rho^3 + c[1]*rho^2 + c[2]*rho + c[3] with rho in mol/m^3 and T in K

higher_order._note: Typo in paper for Aa[1], taking the value from REFPROP 9.1 fluid file.  Also, sign of Ai[0] seems backwards, using value from REFPROP 9.1
